snippet.title: "Great Artists Steal" Trailer
snippet.description:
Handprint Games is collaborating with a local artist, SCR1BBLE, to create a beautiful new hand-drawn indie game: Great Artists Steal.

After a successful Kickstarter campaign in May 2019, we are aiming for initial release on Steam (PC/Mac/Linux) in March 2020.
